text: Mirzazade — surname. *Aydin Mirzazade — is a deputy in the National Assembly of Azerbaijan. *Boyukagha Mirzazade — was a prominent Azerbaijani artist, named People's Artist of the Azerbaijan SSR in 1967. *Khayyam Mirzazade — is an Azerbaijani composer and professor. Category:Surnames
title: Mirzazade
